Entry.EnglishText: A dream...? No, an illusion perhaps?

Entry.JapaneseText: 今のは、ふたりにも 見えたんだね
Entry.EnglishText: So you two saw it this time.

Entry.JapaneseText: ディオス、メルティアって <DIO>くんと、 <MEL>ちゃんのこと……
デリス・カーラーンを 滅ぼしたのは君たち
Entry.EnglishText: You...You were the ones that destroyed Derris Kharlan...

Entry.JapaneseText: あんなのはぼくの カワイイ双子じゃない！
Entry.EnglishText: Those can't be my fair pair of twins!

Entry.JapaneseText: だって、ぼくは、ふたりが うーーんとちっちゃい頃から 知ってるんだかラ！
Entry.EnglishText: I know them very very VERY well! I know they wouldn't do that!

Entry.JapaneseText: ううん…… あれはわたしたち
Entry.EnglishText: It's ok...I know those were we...

Entry.JapaneseText: だよ。オレらは 決着つけなきゃ いけないんだ
Entry.EnglishText: Yeah. It's well due time we settled things right.

Entry.JapaneseText: どうやって 決着をつけるのだ
Entry.EnglishText: And how do you plan to do that?

Entry.JapaneseText: その、うっとうしいの取れよ、 わかってんだ
Entry.EnglishText: You can drop the irritating act!

Entry.JapaneseText: よくも簡単に 決着をつけるなどと 言えたものだ
Entry.EnglishText: How dare you lightly say it's time to set things right.

Entry.JapaneseText: 星を一個まるまる 滅ぼしたくせに
Entry.EnglishText: You are trying to make up for destroying an entire planet?

Entry.JapaneseText: きみたちがやったんでしょ！ 他人事みたいに！
Entry.EnglishText: But it was you who destroyed Derris Kharlan! Stop acting like it's someone else's fault!

Entry.JapaneseText: 悪いのは戦争よ！ わたしたちじゃない！
Entry.EnglishText: It was the war's fault! We aren't at fault!

Entry.JapaneseText: そうだ…… ノルンがおれたちを…… おまえたちを裁いてくれる
Entry.EnglishText: That's right... We...you will be judged by Norn.
Now come. To the place of the trial.

Entry.JapaneseText: あ……逃げた……！ <DIO>、<MEL>、 追わないと……
Entry.EnglishText: They ran away...! And...you two aren't going after them...

Entry.JapaneseText: あれはわたしたちだもん。 どこ行ったかはすぐにわかる
あなたはそこで ただ黙って見てるだけ？
Entry.EnglishText: ...You are going to just stay there silently?

Entry.JapaneseText: 今のこの身は<Red>ダオス城<White>で眠る 我が残存思念の夢に過ぎぬ
Entry.EnglishText: The real Dhaos in this time sleeps in Dhaos' Castle. I am a lingering recollection of dreams long gone.

Entry.JapaneseText: ダオスに 会いに行こうぜ
ダオスに？ どうして！？
決着つける前に、 確かめたいことが あるから、わたしたち
Entry.EnglishText: Before we bring an end to this we need to understand everything.

Entry.JapaneseText: ね？ いいでしょ？ <RND_P>さん
え？ 私？ ……いいっていうか、 確かめたいのは……
Entry.EnglishText: Eh? Me? ...Even if you're asking me, you are decided already.

Entry.JapaneseText: ……ダオスはたぶん、 この世界の南西のはじにある、 <Red>ダオス城<White>にいるよ
Entry.EnglishText: ...Dhaos' Castle is southwest of this world.
